decks.notes: The key concept of this deck is to control the game by ramping up mana quickly using Azusa, Lost but Seeking and various land-based strategies. The deck includes cards that allow the player to play multiple lands per turn, search for specific lands, and recur lands from the graveyard. This enables the player to cast powerful spells and creatures such as Emrakul, the Promised End and Primeval Titan at an accelerated pace. The deck focuses on resource management and land synergy to outvalue opponents and overwhelm them with powerful threats. Additionally, the deck includes a mix of control elements and win conditions to adapt to different matchups and playstyles.
